{"id": 2490, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都有哪些因为「接受别人的好意」而感到的小型不安？", "description": "虽然你是好心，但总有一股欠债压力在我胸中缓缓升腾。", "record_count": 2883, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180730163220N7luOTCPVL50Mop9.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-08-02T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 297216, "content": "当别人说你瘦了的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 296705, "content": "前面那个自己做饭的 我觉得可以自己做饭的真的是好男人啊???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294836}, {"id": 296706, "content": "别人热情安利东西但是我并不感兴趣只想自己找的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137599}, {"id": 296707, "content": "好朋友的男朋友请客的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425606}, {"id": 296708, "content": "以前有过，出去吃饭朋友先去买单的时候，现在慢慢没有不安的情绪了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415269}, {"id": 296710, "content": "装修的时候，同学朋友介绍很多门店设计师，甚至自己就是装修行业的，然而我并不喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423269}, {"id": 296712, "content": "和男朋友在一起的时候希望能互相鼓励彼此，不希望就是好了个对象感觉连朋友都没有了，那样的话，有一天对象离开了，才发现连个说话的人都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425630}, {"id": 296713, "content": "同事热派发她刚出生儿子照片时，想我赞可爱还是丑？我非常不安想打人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423163}, {"id": 296714, "content": "导购太热情（话说这算好意么...）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393244}, {"id": 296715, "content": "不熟悉的同事热心帮助自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425652}, {"id": 296718, "content": "接受不熟的人的帮助", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425672}, {"id": 297232, "content": "你不喜欢的人喜欢你的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427704}, {"id": 296723, "content": "不是很喜欢的同学在毕业后联系，表达思念，感觉愧对别人的感情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410944}, {"id": 298005, "content": "经常分享东西给我吃，我得找机会也给对方吃点啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431999}, {"id": 298008, "content": "不熟的同事请你吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277688}, {"id": 296729, "content": "?️", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425716}, {"id": 296730, "content": "小摊贩要求我买东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425725}, {"id": 296731, "content": "\n有些热爱跟我诉苦的朋友，我虽然看上去很乐观，但有时候承受不了这么多负面情绪，也不值得对我倾诉这么多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425734}, {"id": 296732, "content": "别人邀请你去她家住的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425745}, {"id": 296733, "content": "喜欢你的异性送你东西并且你不怎么喜欢他……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425754}, {"id": 296734, "content": "去旅游 坐公交车没带钢镚 当地不支持公交微信付款码 好心的哥哥直接给 呜呜好感谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425760}, {"id": 296735, "content": "别人给我夹我不喜欢吃的菜的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425764}, {"id": 296736, "content": "加入新公司，跟新同事一起点下午茶，他不肯收aa的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425772}, {"id": 296739, "content": "哪怕只是芝麻点儿大的事，我也是能自己做绝不麻烦别人的人，老有种很怕欠人家的感觉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417486}, {"id": 296741, "content": "做东西时莫名有人凑上来和你搭话然后开始夸你的时候（不好意思赶人走了）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396508}, {"id": 296742, "content": "和朋友出去旅游 相处的方式和饮食习惯不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425854}, {"id": 296745, "content": "不是朋友。却总是帮助我，不求回报的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425862}, {"id": 296748, "content": "做一些明明没有意义的事  但我不做又怕他们说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317306}, {"id": 296749, "content": "不熟的亲戚邀请你到他们家吃饭的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425911}, {"id": 296750, "content": "可能在我感觉是好意的问候在她看来就是不耐烦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425289}, {"id": 296751, "content": "付钱aa最好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327094}, {"id": 296754, "content": "对自己长相不自信，有时候突然被同事热情的夸奖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425947}, {"id": 296755, "content": "怎么没有人对我有那么好心 sigh....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243870}, {"id": 296756, "content": "不太熟的朋友说“这顿算我请吧”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425941}, {"id": 296759, "content": "考虑考虑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425985}, {"id": 296760, "content": "太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395831}, {"id": 296761, "content": "准备提离职的前一天，同组同事说请大家喝下午茶，问我喝什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390820}, {"id": 296762, "content": "不习惯接受别人的帮助，所以所有的吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426017}, {"id": 296763, "content": "别人送给我我完全不需要并且贵重的礼物的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424916}, {"id": 296766, "content": "吃饼干的是妹子么……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530347}, {"id": 296769, "content": "让部门同事陪着我一起加班的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426058}, {"id": 296771, "content": "干什么都觉得用别人的不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422091}, {"id": 296775, "content": "朋友为我买单", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215287}, {"id": 296776, "content": "只是在认真学习，就被同学夸学霸？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426106}, {"id": 296777, "content": "别人送我东西时，都会诚惶诚恐，因为总觉得需要礼尚往来，然后又是一笔开支。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425098}, {"id": 296780, "content": "对我好的，我都感到不安~", "image": "img/option/option/20180803104751No7UnIvOiQGaYscq", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1402798}, {"id": 296781, "content": "吃了好几碗饭  喝了好几杯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423578}, {"id": 301909, "content": "接受的好意是我不想接受的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450831}, {"id": 296552, "content": "我爸平时不能陪我，一直给我塞钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407510}, {"id": 296553, "content": "朋友送的生日礼物太过贵重，其实更希望是一本书就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 139, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956912}]}